{"title":"【算法】排序算法-插入排序","date":"2020-09-21T12:06:02.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Sep 21, 2020","L":"09/21/2020","MM-DD":"09-21"},"link":"2020/09/21/2020-09-21-02","comments":true,"tags":["algorithm"],"updated":"2020-09-21T12:45:45.814Z","content":"<h3 id=\"排序算法-插入排序\">排序算法-插入排序<a title=\"#排序算法-插入排序\" href=\"#排序算法-插入排序\"></a></h3>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>1. 思想</strong></p>\n<p>抓住一个值，然后向左边进行比较大小，如果满足大小，那么进行交换，直到左边没有值为止(相当于插入到了有序元素中)</p>\n<p>然后每一个右值进行同样的操作(开始循环)，直到做完</p>\n<p>整体思想就是，抓住的这一个值，不断往有序元素中找到位置插入，所以叫插入排序</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/2020-09-21-02/insert.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><strong>2. 实现代码(简单粗暴版)</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">func TestInsertSort(t *testing.T)  &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\ttemp :&#x3D; []int&#123;3, 1, 9, 10, 8, 2&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#x2F;&#x2F; 抓住一个值，从左向右抓</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#x2F;&#x2F; 每当抓住一个值后，这个值的左边一定是有序的，右边一定是无序的</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfor i:&#x3D;0; i&lt;len(temp); i++ &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#x2F;&#x2F; 对于第一个值，可以跳过</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tif i &#x3D;&#x3D; 0 &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tcontinue</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#x2F;&#x2F; 开始向该值的左边进行对比，直到这个值插入进有序元素中</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tfor j:&#x3D;i; j&gt;0; j-- &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tif temp[j-1] &gt; temp[j] &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\ttemp[j-1], temp[j] &#x3D; temp[j], temp[j-1]</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t&#125; else &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\tbreak</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfmt.Println(temp)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"【数据库】MySQL 数据库 update A set num=num+ ？ where id=？并发执行情况下存在线程安全问题吗？","link":"2020/09/22/2020-09-22-01"},"next":{"title":"【算法】排序算法-冒泡排序和选择排序","link":"2020/09/21/2020-09-21-01"},"plink":"https://terence.segofun.com/2020/09/21/2020-09-21-02/","toc":[{"id":"排序算法-插入排序","title":"排序算法-插入排序","index":"1"}]}